<item>
            <title>[LU-19050] Support long nidlists in liblustre api</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19050</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Certain &lt;tt&gt;nid&lt;/tt&gt; character arrays in the liblustreapi do not accommodate for nidlists larger than &amp;gt;256 characters due to using &lt;tt&gt;MAX_LINE_LEN&lt;/tt&gt; for its size. This causes further issues in &lt;tt&gt;get_root_path()&lt;/tt&gt; that can result in a buffer overflow during a string copy.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="90029">LU-19050</key>
